<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَيْنَ هَدْيُ الصَّيْدِ؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٠٥٦٢ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ اللَّهُ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ:</span> <span class="c3">{هَدْيًا بَالِغَ الْكَعْبَةِ}</span> <span class="c4">[المائدة: ٩٥]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٠٥٦٣ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ الشَّافِعِيُّ:</span> لَا يُجْزِئُ شَيْءٌ مِنَ الْهَدْيِ حَيَوَانًا كَانَ أَوْ طَعَامًا إِلَّا بِمَكَّةَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>